Thanks to Matthias Blume for developing c-glue-maker.

Demo Mythryl programs in this package are translated from the original C
from following sources:

1. ``OpenGL Programming for the X Window System'', Mark J. Kilgard, 
   Addison Wesley Developers Press, 1996..

2. ``Teach Yourself GTK+ Programming in 21 days'', Donna Martin, et al.
     SAMS publishing.

3. Gtk tutorial from

    http://www.gtk.org/tutorial/index.html

4. SDL homepage

    http://www.libsdl.org/intro/index.html

5. OpenGL tutorial at:

    http://www.libsdl.org/opengl/intro.html

6. mgtk 

    http://mgtk.sourceforge.net

